high_descs: Go to the shelf to your left with the plant on it.
Pick up the pen from the shelf.
Turn around and move forward to cross the room, then turn right at the end of the bed and go to the nightstand ahead.
Put the pen in the mug on the nightstand.
Pick up the mug from the nightstand.
Turn around and move forward to the end of the bed, then turn left and return to the shelf ahead.
Put the mug on the shelf in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a pen in it on the shelf.

turn around and walk past the foot of the bed on your right, then turn right and walk over to the night stand on the left side of the bed
place the pencil inside a cup on the nightstand
pick up the cup with the pencil in it off of the nightstand

place the cup on top of the cabinet

high_descs: Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and walk over to the white dresser.
Pick up the black pen off of the white dresser.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then turn right and walk up to the small wooden table.
Put the pen in the white mug on the small wooden table.
Pick up the white mug with the pen in it off of the wooden table.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the white dresser.
Put the mug with the pen in it on the dresser in front of the laptop.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a pen in it on a white dresser.
